snippet.title: PSX Longplay [335] Frenzy!
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

Very much an obscured title. It's hard to find any info about this game, and I couldn't find a video footage of it anywhere. The levels and enemies are loosely based on movie titles and references. It was released only in Europe. The game is full of glitches and at times it's impossibly hard, with 'enemies' that looks like a glitch and kills you instantly. I had to rush through the snow level because of a bug. Overall, no wonder it's not a known game. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
